                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿جُندٖ﴾: جَيشٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "36:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿صَيۡحَةٗ﴾: صَوْتاً مُهلِكاً مِنَ السَّماءِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿خَٰمِدُونَ﴾: مَيِّتُونَ لا حَرَاكَ فِيهِم.</h2>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "36:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَسۡتَهۡزِءُونَ﴾: يَسْخَرُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "36:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مِنَ ٱلۡقُرُونِ﴾: مِنَ الأُمَمِ الخالِيةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "36:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مُحۡضَرُونَ﴾: نُحْضِرُهُم للحسابِ والجزاءِ.</h2>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "36:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَءَايَةٞ لَّهُمُ﴾: دَلَالةٌ لَهُم.</h2>\n<h2>﴿ٱلۡأَرۡضُ ٱلۡمَيۡتَةُ﴾: هي الَّتي لا نَبَاتَ فِيها.</h2>\n<p>﴿أَحۡيَيۡنَٰهَا﴾: أي: بإنْزالِ المطرِ عَلَيها وإخراجِ النَّباتِ منها.</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "36:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿جَنَّٰتٖ﴾: بَسَاتِينَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَجَّرۡنَا﴾: شَقَقْنا.</h2>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
